							Começar Agora
						</a>
					</div>
					<div class="plan-card">
						<div class="plan-header">
							<h3>Semestral</h3>
							<div class="price">
								<span class="currency">R$</span>
								<span class="amount">67</span>
								<span class="period">/mês</span>
